lead_paragraph: Ireland assistant manager Roy Keane expressed his frustration at his team's lethargic performance in the loss to Belarus in a Euro 2016 warm-up, saying he wanted to kill some of his players.

headline.print_headline: Ireland's Keane Vents Frustration After Belarus Loss
